                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6076" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0919</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8432 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谋“定”后“算”：北方管道公司成本预算转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Deciding “Quota” Before “Budget”: The Transformation of Cost Budget System of Northern Pipeline Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">付代红，邵洁，苏慧敏，王方正</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（华东）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国家管网集团北方管道有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北方管道公司；零基预算；成本定额；管理体系；业财融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Northern Pipeline Company; Zero-based budgeting; cost quota; management system; integration of business and finance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为国内最具代表性的长输油气管道运营企业之一，北方管道公司的成本预算管理面临成本构成复杂、投入产出模糊、定额体系不全、业务量参数不清晰等诸多困难。北方管道公司以成本定额编制为突破点，创新定额管理思路，引入平台思维模式，通过建立规范的制度、方法和工具体系，引导财务部门、业务处室和实体单位转换角色、合作共赢，使得成本定额编制工作科学、高效、实用。经过数年的持续努力，形成了完善的成本定额体系，保障了零基预算的落地实施，有效实现了成本控制，显著提升了管理效率。本案例从总会计师余总的视角，按照“困境—突破—架构—实施—效果”的逻辑体系，介绍了北方管道公司通过改革成本定额管理体系而推动成本预算转型的全过程，留下了从零基预算、成本定额、业财融合等角度进行深度分析和讨论的空间。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As one of the most representative long-distance oil and gas pipeline operators in China, the cost budget management of Northern Pipeline Company is faced with many difficulties, such as complex cost structure, fuzzy input-output, incomplete quota system, unclear parameters. The company have adopted cost quota as breakthrough point, while innovated cost quota management and introduced platform thinking. Through the establishment of standard system, methods and tools, the financial department, business department and entity unit of the company have switched roles and achieved win-win cooperation, leading to a scientific, efficient and practical process. After years of continuous efforts, a sound cost quota system has been formed to ensure the implementation of zero-based budgeting, realization of cost control and improvement of management efficiency. This case introduces the reformation process of cost quota system and the transformation of cost budget in Northern Pipeline Company from the perspective of chief accountant, Yu, via the logic of &quot;dilemma, breakthrough, construction, implementation and effect&quot;, leaving discussion and analysis space for the zero-base budget, cost quota and integration of business and finance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《成本管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">预算管理、定额管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
